#       `export AWS_REGION=your-aws-region`
#       (For Windows, use `set` instead of `export`)
#    e. Run the app: `flask run` or `python app.py`

# 3. Deployment on EC2 using Docker:
#    a. SSH into your EC2 instance.
#    b. Install Docker:
#       `sudo yum update -y` (Amazon Linux) or `sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get install docker.io -y` (Ubuntu)
#       `sudo systemctl start docker`
#       `sudo usermod -aG docker ec2-user` (or ubuntu)
#       `newgrp docker` (or log out and back in)
#    c. Copy your project files (app.py, requirements.txt, templates/, Dockerfile) to the EC2 instance.
